  <tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="left" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
    Used with the bandage skill to quickly heal characters.  This is the substitute for the non-healing classes for healing spells, although it's far more primitive.
		</font>
    </td>
  </tr>
  
