			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just a few things about bandages:<BR>
<BR>
Magicians can conjure them nearly at will, and can be very useful for your party when the clerics become exhausted. I suggest that you magicians keep a few onhand so that you can practice using them when it is not time-critical.<BR>
<BR>
Also, bandages can only be used to heal up to half of your total hitpoints.  I found this out the hard way.<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
