				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				A note one the bandages and the bandaging skill, and on magicians you heal 1 point for every 4 you have in the bandaging skill. <BR>
Magicians summon 1 bandage per 2 lvls so higher lvl mages can summon a LOT of them and distribute them to any in the party who have the skill. Three people with good bandaging skills can heal a wounded comrade to 1/2 hp rather quickly
				</font>
			</td>

