				You can give bandages to Joogl Hunneybugger by the druid ring in Misty Thicket. To get there-as you enter MT from Rivervale, turn left, its a little hut a ways down by the wall. Give hundreds to him, raises your faction with Mayor and Sheriff, etc. in RV, to get the Squad Ring.<BR>
<BR>
Also, you have a bind wound skill, you need bandages to use it, use it up to half health. The higher the skill the more HP you recover per bandaging.
